auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Clearest Images of Jupiter ever taken 

These beautifully real images are some of the closest images of Jupiter. Jupiter is the fifth planet from the Sun and the largest in the Solar System. It is a gas giant with a mass more than two and a half times that of all the other planets in the Solar System combined, but slightly less than one-thousandth the mass of the Sun. The original image was captured by JunoCam, the camera on NASA's Juno mission in orbit around Jupiter. This image was taken on Juno's 22nd close pass by Jupiter on Sept. 12, 2019</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XT9VSMq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G8xinOj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lWPUUqZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/urmzwWr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KSJVT5k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bvjXL8c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jAn2SCb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HPZnvfj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PVCUDWZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3AUf6vc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zOaUMcn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/y5f4SXi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRainbowegoSweet007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Princess Ingrid Alexandra of Norway turns 18</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/D4RuYIN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iaLoNaL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Princess of Norway, Ingrid Alexandra, turns 18 today. Hurray and congratulations! 

She is the second in line to the norwegian throne, following her father Crown  Prince Haakon, and King Harald.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ChW82zN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For her 18th birthday, she got a tour of the parliament...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Asmbtyz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...the supreme court of Norway...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DnLRUJK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...and a visit to the prime minister. Thus, visiting the three branches of government in Norway: The legislative, executive and judicial.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U6OhjmU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The day she becomes queen, she will also be the highest ranking in the norwegian military. Leading up to her 18th birthday, she also visited the military.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YKnCT3A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>..where she also got to fly a fighter jet. (Yes, she was in control of the plane for a while.)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/notP4pM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They grow up so fast. Happy birthday!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/D4RuYIN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[frosketosk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Treasonous sympathies of Clarence Thomas</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/x7PfUYC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jMXWkhO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/x7PfUYC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mugjunk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hit 3 years sober yesterday.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gYs